{"tid":2191660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"FNC新男團成員被爆意淫防彈JIMIN：玩佢春袋玩足7個鐘","createTime":"2020-09-06T14:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T14:22:37.000Z","uid":112747,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"048340384c5c60102dbf20cadb7cdfa2f2dacea3","tid":2191660,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:51:25.000Z","msg":"新人男偶像被爆「EXO黑粉、意淫JIMIN」 亮相才一天手寫信道歉了<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1802047#ixzz6XGNO6sO6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1802047%23ixzz6XGNO6sO6&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4sg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=5430c34f\" target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1802047#ixzz6XGNO6sO6</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓經紀公司FNC娛樂即將推出新男團「P1harmony」，近來正陸續公布組合成員，沒想到其中韓裔加拿大籍成員Keeho（기호）亮相才不到一天，就被挖出大量黑歷史。包括他其實是著名的「EXO黑粉」，還曾經開非裔女性玩笑，引爆軒然大波後，Keeho發表了手寫信，FNC則以聲明說明實情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5121/d5121140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5121%2Fd5121140.jpg&h=e0f4b616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKeeho所經營帳號，被翻出曾有對JIMIN性幻想的貼文<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5121/d5121148.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5121%2Fd5121148.jpg&h=3311ada3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得罪army,唔退團依團都唔駛出道lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ecd067738801471dca8e41c3bcec76f3be94f5","tid":2191660,"uid":7903,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"對Jimin有性幻想算唔算係一個army"},{"pid":"15b56eb1dcfc08e1ae2c80a582aecb7a57d84a16","tid":2191660,"uid":89931,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"army姐"},{"pid":"8b24446c31ecd434fa5b113317c54f20b282f717","tid":2191660,"uid":37196,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:13:36.000Z","msg":"FNC咁上下啦"},{"pid":"643f8f01a8ed5e38